Package textInterpret

Class Token

java.lang.Object
textInterpret.Token
Direct Known Subclasses:
Token.BracketCloseToken, Token.BracketOpenToken, Token.CommaToken, Token.EndToken, Token.FuncToken, Token.InfixToken, Token.UnaryToken, Token.VarToken
public class Token
extends java.lang.Object
Container class for various tokens used in expression parsing. Accessor and mutator methods are provided to allow getting and setting various variables related to different types of tokens.

Token provides no public constructor, and throws TokenTypeMismatchException when getter or setter methods are called. Instantiable subclasses override this behaviour when appropriate.

Author:
kieran
See Also:
